{
  "metadata": {
    "id": "balato",
    "name": "balato",
    "author": [
      "Cinnabruh"
    ],
    "description": "made ts with joker forge so its might be buggy\nWelcome one and all to balato!\nunbalanced cards, silly goofs, damn booster packs for vouchers, a whole new rarity and a new series of jokers! the \"tarnished\" jokers are basically unbalanced versions of base jokers and i thought it would be funny to add lore!\n\nOn march 3rd, 2026, photograph and hanging chad were in a abandoned museum, when they discovered an ancient curse trapped in a box. the cursed contained an entity that acted like parasite that took over hanging chad and making him go insane. this curse/entity/infection spread worldwide, attacking the easy targets like blueprint and jolly joker. blueprint was he first to notify baron, but 5 days later, it was too late. baron went missing.",
    "prefix": "balato",
    "main_file": "main.lua",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "priority": 0,
    "badge_colour": "ffffff",
    "badge_text_colour": "FF3333",
    "display_name": "balato",
    "dependencies": [
      "Steamodded (>=1.0.0~BETA-0827c)",
      "Talisman"
    ],
